OL,3,CTasers issued to some prison officers
OL,4,Cafter attack at County Durham jail
OL,6,FSome specialist prison officers are
OL,7,Fbeing equipped with Tasers from today
OL,8,F(Monday 28 July), following an attack
OL,9,Fat HMP Frankland in County Durham in
OL,10,FApril.
OL,12,FThe Justice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,13,Fhas said she is "determined to keep
OL,14,Fprison staff safe", as the Government
OL,15,Faims to clamp down on record levels of
OL,16,Fviolence.
