OL,3,CTasers issued to some prison officers
OL,4,Cafter attack at County Durham jail
OL,6,FThe Taser trial follows an incident at
OL,7,FHMP Frankland in April this year, when
OL,8,FManchester Arena plotter Hashem Abedi
OL,9,Ftargeted prison staff with boiling oil
OL,10,Fand homemade weapons in a planned
OL,11,Fambush.
OL,13,FFour prison officers were injured,
OL,14,Fwith three of them taken to hospital.
OL,16,FMs Mahmood has admitted this attack
OL,17,Fhas sped up the trial of Tasers,
OL,18,Fsaying the incident "has really forced
OL,19,Fthe pace on further roll-out of these
OL,20,Fmeasures."
