OL,3,CTasers issued to some prison officers
OL,4,Cafter attack at County Durham jail
OL,6,FSpecialist officers from the
OL,7,FOperational Response and Resilience
OL,8,FUnit based in Kidlington, Oxfordshire,
OL,9,Fand Doncaster, South Yorkshire, will
OL,10,Fbe the first to become equipped with
OL,11,FTasers.
OL,13,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,14,Fattended the base in Kidlington last
OL,15,FThursday, when officers demonstrated
OL,16,Fhow they would use Tasers on violent
OL,17,Finmates in scenarios where there is a
OL,18,Fsignificant threat to safety ` such as
OL,19,Fhostage situations or riots.
