OL,3,CTasers issued to some prison officers
OL,4,Cafter attack at County Durham jail
OL,6,FThe trial will run until enough data
OL,7,Fhas been collected to determine if
OL,8,FTasers should be more widely used,
OL,9,Faccording the Ministry of Justice `
OL,10,Fbut Ms Mahmood said she hoped to have
OL,11,Fupdates in the autumn.
OL,13,FIt comes after rates of assaults on
OL,14,Fprison staff reached record levels
OL,15,Flast year, rising by 13% in the 12
OL,16,Fmonths up to December 2024, according
OL,17,Fto Government data.
