OL,3,CTasers issued to some prison officers
OL,4,Cafter attack at County Durham jail
OL,6,FThere were also 10,496 assaults on
OL,7,Fstaff in the 12 months to September
OL,8,F2024 ` a 23% increase from the
OL,9,Fprevious 12 months and a new peak.
OL,11,FThe Tasers will be worn by officers on
OL,12,Ftheir tactical vest in a secure
OL,13,Fholster, making the weapon visible to
OL,14,Finmates as a deterrent, officers told
OL,15,FMs Mahmood last week.
OL,17,FThe Prison Officers' Association (POA)
OL,18,Fsaid it welcomed the move, but added
OL,19,Fthe Government needed to address the
OL,20,Froots of violence in jail.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
