OL,3,CTasers issued to some prison officers
OL,4,Cafter attack at County Durham jail
OL,6,F"The POA will always support any
OL,7,Finitiative that will help protect our
OL,8,Fmembers," a spokesperson for the trade
OL,9,Funion said.
OL,11,F"However, as welcome as this
OL,12,Finitiative is, we need to address the
OL,13,Freasons why prison officers need
OL,14,FTasers in the first place.
OL,16,F"Violence in our prisons is out of
OL,17,Fcontrol and apathetic prison managers
OL,18,Fwould rather put the prison regime
OL,19,Fbefore the safety of their staff.
